        Department of Mathematics and Computer Science at Chulalongkorn
        University was founded in the late 30â€™s as the first mathematics
        department in the nation. Since then it has grown up and became the
        academic foundation and root of several other mathematics departments in
        Thailand.
      </p>
      <p class="font-light">
